Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:34.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune had come into possession\Nof the Kasumiohji Clan's Bakkouto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to attain the power to\Nbecome the strongest Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:42.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira put everything he\Nhad on the line to challenge Kibune,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who only believed in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After an intense battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:50.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira was finally able to defeat Kifune,\Nwho had shown his true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:55.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Ichigo and his friends\Nentered the Kasumiohji mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:57.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to rescue Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:02:01.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They battled against\NHitsugaya and Squad 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kurosaki!\NLeave this place to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:08.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:09.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reign over the frosted heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sever, Raika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the same time, having obtained
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune's Bakkouto as proof of treason,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:37.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Genryusai finally gave out the order\Nto put down the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It has come to light that there were\Nsuspicious acts of high treason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,found against\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All squads of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:53.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will enter the Kasumiohji mansion\Nimmediately and secure this evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruffian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu… Do you know\Nwhere Rurichiyo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe…the one in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:13.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi didn't allow us\Nto go near there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, which way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rurichiyo, where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For generations, the Kasumiohji Clan\Nhas forged and delivered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:32.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,heirloom swords to the royal families\Nthat were used for ceremonial purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The techniques they use\Nwere kept strictly in-house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:41.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, they have maintained\Nthe right of immunity for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, certain factions\Nwithin the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,have taken advantage of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that we cannot\N easily interfere with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and went off to break the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:53.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,taboo of producing a\N dangerous blade such as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know this with certainty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it is only natural that we make our move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain, did you expect this outcome
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when the Substitute Soul Reaper…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:16.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assigning Captain Kuchiki\Nof Squad 6 to lead the raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:16.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:31.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain Yamamoto\Nhas changed his orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:37.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He has ordered all Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads to take control of our clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:46.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to,\N"That will never happen"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"I guarantee your safety,"\Nhe said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the reason why I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,went along with his plan,\N even at great risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have no choice\Nbut to use these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:03.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A change of orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:07.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Our orders are to\Nseize the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the complete opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not have any details yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem we don't\Nhave to fight any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Kasumiohji Clan\Nassassins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:38.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These men are using\Na blade called the Bakkouto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakkouto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Kasumiohji Clan's\Ndark secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So we don't need\Nto hold back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Growl, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:06.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it with them?!\NDon't they feel any pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:16.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain has given\Nthe order to raid this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kasumiohji Clan is\Nsuspected of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His orders are to assist\Nthe Substitute Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you is next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be using\Nquite unusual swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:49.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those things won't\Nmake you a match for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the other\Nsquads out do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them the pride of Squad 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Evidence of forbidden techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,connected with treason\N have been found within
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our orders are to\Ntake control immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:21.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad things didn't drag on\Nany further, Captain Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How far does this continue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a huge mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to keep\Ngoing as far as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:41.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:03.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean their swords are all Bakkoutos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Their souls have been\Ntaken over by their swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 33: Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Renji did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The order was given to raid\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:31.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that bastard Kumoi\Ndecided to bring out his secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:36.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Who'd have imagined they'd\Nproduce so many Bakkoutos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia… Take Shu\Nand go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The intense security means
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that there's something\N important up ahead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I'll leave this place to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:59.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!\NI'll take you on all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems\Nto have started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki and the others\Nmight have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this commotion\Nto rescue Lady Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've sensed it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Man…\NWhat is up with these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ugly way they fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't something\Nbe done about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The way they fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like throwing away their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more precisely,\Nthey have lost their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:54.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So this must be the power of\Nthose swords called the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:58.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're wrong to think they can\Nstop us with something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this was all part of\Nthe Head Captain's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head Captain's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:13.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kasumiohji Clan is an aristocracy\Nwith a special status.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can interfere with them except
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:16.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under extraordinary circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head Captain already had
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,his hands on information\N that the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,was up to no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By sheer coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki became involved,\N so he used him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:33.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows just how much\Nhe trusted in their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a wily old fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir Kumoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:48.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! Don't leave your posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the main gate and building have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,been occupied by the Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:58.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is still going on\N in the garden, but we cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,hold them much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need is for them\Nto buy me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just until I can get inside\Nthe Bakkouto workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:09.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm there…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:12.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kumoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Reapers are\N in the Bakkouto workshop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier there was bestowed\Non us by a royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be broken by\Nthe likes of the Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:50.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Jushiro Ukitake, Squad 13 Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Thirteen Court Guard Squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now conduct\Nan inspection of the premises!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want everyone to remain\Nwhere you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away\Nthis way, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:14.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soi Fon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:21.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. That was a wonderful job\Nof breaking through the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:27.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…the barrier around the workshop\Nwas an extraordinary one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn how to break through
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,such a powerful barrier, Lady Yoruichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,From a man who was angry\Nwith the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for interfering with his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:43.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse those Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kumoi,\Nwe have nowhere else to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess!\NBring Rurichiyo to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:56.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this,\Nour only choice is to use her as a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you guys!\NYou'll die if you keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:27.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reached a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:41.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this way was\Nthe most suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These people are\NRuricchi's attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious men have\Ntaken Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:02.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So Ruricchi was here after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:07.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She returned a while ago\Nand was locked up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:10.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told to look after her here,\Nand stayed with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The man standing guard\Nopened that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden passageway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kumoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you until now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:36.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…I had many things\Nto look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:40.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:43.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nhave stormed the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They have already taken control of\Nmuch of the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We must have you explain to them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by going to the front lines, Sir Kumoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "a problem"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kumoi…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we are not aware
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:05.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of what you are doing behind our backs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Lady Rturichiyo!\N– Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this,\NSir Kumoi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:20.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done\Nto Lady Rurichiyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Sir Kumoi!\N– Sir Kumoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:31.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:34.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill the vassals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:44.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the princess of this clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can go unpunished\Nfor killing my vassals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This clan belongs to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing more than\Na mere hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I a hostage for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it that you are afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose\Nam I being treated like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:19.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever stop talking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:19.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia! Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo is close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:28.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So she was here after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She climbed up here\Nvia a shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:42.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:50.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!\NPut me down more gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:55.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thankful\Nthat I'm allowing you to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a mere hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot judge what\NI should be thankful for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:05.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I give you\Na little lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:26.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait,\NRurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What in heaven's name\Ntook you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…sorry.\NI'll rescue you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking Rurichiyo back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Lady Rurichiyo!\N– Ruricchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuchiki! And Sir Shu too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come near me, and she dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:16.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:21.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyokaku Kumoi!\NWhat is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you create a weapon\Nlike the Bakkouto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:33.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He is planning to use the Bakkouto\Nto disrupt Soul Society
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:36.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and grab power as the leader\Nof the noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:42.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard. You did this\Nto Rurichiyo just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate the opposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is one of the conditions for victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:54.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your forgiveness,\Nyou idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:59.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader of the noble family?\NAbsurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means a short life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:05.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stand on top of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:08.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For that purpose,\NI will do anything it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:34.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai, this guy seems to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:43.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,be the mastermind of this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:50.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:19.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've killed the mastermind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:29.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll never know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:49.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that…\Nsupposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:18.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything just as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:21.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So why is it only me that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:25.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi and Captain Amagai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:23.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Out past the fields laid darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:25.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A life fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:27.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Many years have\Npassed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:34.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have come back\Nto this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:38.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:53.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with these guests' faces?\NI can't get through this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:57.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to eat snackies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:00.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:02.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:04.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}